    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "1920" ;
    dc:creator "Amorim, Dalton De Souza; Oliveira, Sarah Siqueira" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "Eleven new species of the genus Cluzobra Edwards (Diptera, Mycetophilidae, Sciophilinae) from the Atlantic Forest of Brazil" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184698>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184700> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184698>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 10. Wings of Cluzobra species. 5. Cluzobra triocellata, sp. n. 6. Cluzobra accola, sp. n. 7. Cluzobra lanei Edwards, specimen from Anastácio, State of São Paulo. 8. Cluzobra claripennis, sp. n. 9. Cluzobra papaveroi, sp. n. 10. Cluzobra coptolithus, sp. n., paratype from Recife, State of Pernambuco." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184700>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 22. Male terminalia of Cluzobra species. 20. Cluzobra triocellata, sp. n., lateral view. 21. Cluzobra accola, sp. n., ventral view. 22. Same, syngonocoxite plate removed. Abbreviations: ae, aedeagus; ce, cercus; sg, syngonocoxite; gs, gonostyle; s 8, sternite 8; t 8, tergite 8; t 9, tergite 9." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

